bio.tool description: This is a modified copy of MS-FINDER with source code modifications to make the tool accessible in Galaxy.MS-FINDER - software for structure elucidation of unknown spectra with hydrogen rearrangement (HR) rulesThe program supports molecular formula prediction, metabolie class prediction, and structure elucidation for EI-MS and MS/MS spectra, and the assembly is licensed under the CC-BY 4.0.
